Prompt Builder
Simplify your users’ daily tasks by integrating generative-AI powered by prompt templates into their workflow. Create, test, revise, customize, and manage prompt templates that incorporate your CRM data from merge fields.

In July's release, Prompt Builder introduces Record Snapshots, a new grounding capability that adds relevant data from the user’s page layout for an object with one click. It also supports free text inputs in flex prompt templates, allowing you to include free text input fields just like merge fields or other resources.

This feature enables handling multiple scenarios where your prompt template must receive free text as input. Additionally, you can now see when the Einstein Trust layer masks sensitive data by sending placeholder text, with a summary of all masked data available in the Data Masking Details dialog. Prompt Builder also provides a visual alert for any harmful responses from the LLM, ensuring your responses are nontoxic and inclusive.
title: Prompt Builder Features in Salesforce Summer '24 Release
